---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <title>Survey Service Areas in Flintshire &amp; Chester | LEM</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="See the Flintshire, Chester and Cheshire locations covered by LEM Building Surveying Ltd. Find out how to book a survey in your area."
    />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://www.lembuildingsurveying.co.uk/areas" />
    <meta
      property="og:title"
      content="Survey Service Areas in Flintshire &amp; Chester | LEM"
    />
    <meta
      property="og:description"
      content="Discover the towns and villages served by LEM Building Surveying Ltd and access location-specific guidance for booking a survey."
    />
    <meta
      property="og:url"
      content="https://www.lembuildingsurveying.co.uk/areas"
    />
    <meta
      property="og:image"
      content="https://www.lembuildingsurveying.co.uk/logo-sticker.png"
    />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta
      name="twitter:title"
      content="Survey Service Areas in Flintshire &amp; Chester | LEM"
    />
    <meta
      name="twitter:description"
      content="Book home surveys, damp reports and EPCs across Flintshire, Chester and neighbouring Cheshire towns."
    />
    <meta
      name="twitter:url"
      content="https://www.lembuildingsurveying.co.uk/areas"
    />
    <meta
      name="twitter:image"
      content="https://www.lembuildingsurveying.co.uk/logo-sticker.png"
    />
  </Fragment>

  <main class="box-container">
    <h1>Service Areas</h1>
    <p>
      LEM Building Surveying Ltd is based in Connah’s Quay and supports homeowners, landlords
      and investors throughout Flintshire, Chester, Cheshire and parts of the North West.
      From terraced housing in Saltney to rural properties around Tarporley, we bring local
      knowledge and independent advice to every inspection.
    </p>

    <h2>Find Your Town or Village</h2>
    <p>
      Visit the <a href="/local-surveys.html">Areas We Cover</a> page for a full directory of
      locations. Each page highlights recent projects, typical survey types and practical tips
      for booking in that area.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        Explore location guides for Chester neighbourhoods including Hoole, Vicars Cross and
        Westminster Park.
      </li>
      <li>
        Review coverage across Flintshire—from Buckley and Mold to coastal towns such as
        Holywell and Flint.
      </li>
      <li>
        Check regional availability if you are purchasing in Cheshire or the wider North West.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Need to Confirm Availability?</h2>
    <p>
      If you are unsure whether we cover your property, send the postcode and a brief note
      about the service required. We will respond quickly with a quote or a recommendation for
      a trusted surveyor if we cannot assist.
    </p>
    <div class="cta-section">
      <a class="cta-button" href="/enquiry.html">Request a Quote</a>
      <a class="secondary-button" href="/contact.html">Speak to a Surveyor</a>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
